# Cloudflare Pages redirects/rewrites.
#
# blog.husrihtlaefan.org must first be attached to this Pages project as a
# custom domain (dashboard → the project → Custom domains → add
# blog.husrihtlaefan.org) — see CLOUDFLARE_SETUP.md. Once attached, the rule
# below rewrites only the subdomain's ROOT to the blogroll page; every other
# path (css/, js/, /api/*, post hashes) resolves normally on that host too.
https://blog.husrihtlaefan.org/ /blog.html 200
https://app.husrihtlaefan.org/ /app.html 200
https://client.husrihtlaefan.org/ /view.html 200
